              <p class="lead">Emissary helps your company grow by engaging with clients without limits having a team to manage communication. We makes it easy to connect with clients while ignoring APIs and other complex integrations that are not relavent for busy professionals. </p>
              <br>
            </header>

            <div class="row gap-y text-center">

              <div class="col-md-6 col-xl-4 feature-1">
                <p class="feature-icon lead-8 text-primary"><i class="icon-megaphone"></i></p>
                <h5>Broadcasts (Bulk Messaging)</h5>
                <p class="text-muted">Broadcast notifications or alerts to all your clients or a segment</p>
              </div>

              <div class="col-md-6 col-xl-4 feature-1">
                <p class="feature-icon lead-8 text-primary"><i class="icon-chat"></i></p>
                <h5>2-Way Private Messageing</h5>
                <p class="text-muted">Build rapport with your clients, by responding to messages and building relationships </p>
              </div>

              <div class="col-md-6 col-xl-4 feature-1">
                <p class="feature-icon lead-8 text-primary"><i class="icon-layers"></i></p>
                <h5>Unlimited Message Templates and Client Contacts</h5>
                <p class="text-muted">Create message templates for common responses are automated messages you would like to send</p>
              </div>

            </div>
           
            <div class="row gap-y text-center">

              <div class="col-md-6 col-xl-4 feature-1">
                <p class="feature-icon lead-8 text-primary"><i class="icon-adjustments"></i></p>
