                <p class="text-muted">Use the IF-This-Then-That system(similar to Zapier) to help automate your messages </p>
              </div>

              <div class="col-md-6 col-xl-4 feature-1">
                <p class="feature-icon lead-8 text-primary"><i class="icon-pricetags"></i></p>
                <h5>Unlimited Segmentation and Tags</h5>
                <p class="text-muted">Use the applications to segment and tag your contacts for better management</p>
              </div>

              <div class="col-md-6 col-xl-4 feature-1">
                <p class="feature-icon lead-8 text-primary"><i class="icon-presentation"></i></p>
                <h5>Monthly Reporting</h5>
                <p class="text-muted">I send you reports regularly, to keep you in the loop of what messages will be sent and what was sent.</p>
              </div>

            </div>

          </div>
        </section>


