                  <div>
                    <i class="fa fa-diamond fs-25 pt-4 text-primary"></i>
                  </div>

                  <div>
                    <h5>Salon and Beauty</h5>
                    <p>Have a gap in your calendar, remind customers to come in for a treatment or session </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>


              <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4">
                <div class="flexbox gap-items-4">
                  <div>
                    <i class="fa fa-futbol-o  fs-25 pt-4 text-primary"></i>
                  </div>

                  <div>
                    <h5>Fitness and Recreation</h5>
