<section class="section" id="section-faq">
                    <div class="container">
                      <header class="section-header">
                        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                        <hr>
                        <p class="lead">Drop us an email if you couldn't find an answers to your question in the following list.</p>
                      </header>


                      <div class="row gap-y gap-3">

                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                          <h6 class="fw-400">What happens when my sms credits run out?</h6>
                          <p>You will recieve warning emails before it is predicted to run out, you can also purchase additional sms credits within the application</p>
                        </div>


                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                          <h6 class="fw-400">What is the sign up process?</h6>
                          <p>You will sign up on and choose a plan on this website. Once you successfuly paid, you will recieve an Email with you login details, a few notes about the app and then you can start sending messages to your clients</p>
                        </div>


                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                          <h6 class="fw-400">Do you offer free plans?</h6>
                          <p>I am a solo developer trying to make a living and would find it difficult to currently afford it</p>
                        </div>


